      <td><p class="mini"><a href="http://libraries.mit.edu/ordering/index.html" title="http://libraries.mit.edu/ordering/index.html">Borrowing &amp; Ordering</a> &gt; <a href="http://libraries.mit.edu/ordering/non-mit-access/harvard.html" title="http://libraries.mit.edu/ordering/non-mit-access/harvard.html">Access to non-MIT libraries: Harvard</a> &gt;Frances Loeb Library</p>
        <h2><font color="#666666"><a name="content"></a>Access to non-MIT libraries for MIT community members</font></h2>
        <h3>Harvard Libraries</h3>
        <h2>Francis Loeb Library<em> (Graduate School of Design)</em><br>Special Borrower Card Application</h2>
        <p>If your work requires extensive use of resources not available at MIT, you may qualify for access to the <a href="http://www.gsd.harvard.edu/loeb_library/index.html">Frances Loeb Library</a> (Graduate School of Design). </p>
        <table width="533" border="1" cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0">
          <tr>
            <td width="144" valign="middle" bgcolor="#CCCCCC"><strong>Privileges:</strong></td>
            <td width="177" valign="middle" bgcolor="#CCCCCC"><strong>Status:</strong></td>
            <td width="174" valign="middle" bgcolor="#CCCCCC"><p><strong>Card valid from:</strong></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Borrowing privileges</td>
            <td>Faculty &amp; Research Staff </td>
            <td>September 1 &ndash; August 31 </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Borrowing privileges</td>
            <td>Graduate  Students </td>
            <td>September 1 &ndash; May 31* </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Room use only</td>
            <td>Undergraduate students</td>
            <td><p>N/A</p></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <p>*For summer access, graduate students may reapply for a Special Borrower Card, valid for one year, beginning June 1. (The Harvard summer letter is no longer needed.)</p>
        <form name="loeb" id="loeb" action="https://libraries.mit.edu/hcl/submitapp-new.php" method="post">
          <input name="hidden" type="hidden"
                id="eppn"
