          "
          >
                  <fieldset>
                    You will receive a response as soon as possible, and no later than 5:00pm the next business day. If you need immediate access to Frances Loeb Library, please bring your MIT ID to the service desk at Barker, Dewey, Hayden, or Rotch Libraries, and fill out the appropriate forms at the desk.
  <p><em>Please note:</em> If you have a current Harvard College Library Special Borrower Card or have recently applied for one, you do not need to re-apply for Loeb Library privileges. The HCL Special Borrower Card can be used for Loeb Library access and borrowing.</p>
